<c.magenta>못 맞출겁니다.</c>

00:30:40.407 --> 00:30:41.642 align:middle line:0
<c.magenta>바로 Metal 2입니다.</c>

00:30:42.876 --> 00:30:46.213 align:middle line:0
<c.magenta>Metal 2는 정말 빠릅니다.</c>

00:30:46.280 --> 00:30:49.383 align:middle line:0
