00:32:19.506 --> 00:32:21.542 align:middle line:-2
<c.magenta>적합하도록 앱을</c>
<c.magenta>튜닝할 수 있습니다.</c>

00:32:21.608 --> 00:32:23.410 align:middle line:-2
<c.magenta>그리고 수개월</c>
