01:48:41.154 --> 01:48:42.623 align:middle line:-1
<c.magenta>중첩 폴더, 스프링로딩,</c>

01:48:42.689 --> 01:48:46.360 align:middle line:-2
<c.magenta>목록뷰, 즐겨찾기,</c>
